The paper deals with deep learning-based image registration, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of generative adversarial networks (GANs) and transfer learning also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The experiments involve medical images, which could fall under multimedia (cs.MM) or neural networks (cs.NE) sub-categories.
